title: Cinch Men's Silver Label Slim-Fit Jean
description: Silver label is one cinch's newest additions in a straight leg jean. This jean has a relaxed waist with a mid-rise for all day comfort. Copper oxide cinch embossed rivets, non-ratcheting zipper slider and double stitched reinforced felled seam on the inside of the legs to eliminate chafing. The fitted hip, thigh, and knee end in a straight leg with a 17 1/4 inch opening. The five-pocket, 100 percent cotton denim is pre-shrunk and fits as good tomorrow as it does today.
